{"id":545214,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/11/【立此存照】精准删帖/","date":"2016-11-24T05:19:03Z","modified":"2016-11-24T04:12:42Z","title":"【立此存照】精准删帖","content":"<blockquote><p><a href=\"http://weibo.com/1375242654/EiKLupslz\" target=\"_blank\">@汉唐风烟</a>：“精准扶贫”能不能做到不知道，不过，“精准删帖”渣浪肯定是做到了。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://weibo.com/1827652007/EiZXH8ITr\" target=\"_blank\">@于建嵘</a>: 我对自己写的东西违反了“相关法律法规和政策”，向读者们致歉。</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/51f8899ejw1fa13x3iplpj20hs0vkadr.jpeg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-545215\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/51f8899ejw1fa13x3iplpj20hs0vkadr.jpeg\" alt=\"51f8899ejw1fa13x3iplpj20hs0vkadr\" width=\"400\" height=\"710\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/51f8899ejw1fa13x3iplpj20hs0vkadr.jpeg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/51f8899ejw1fa13x3iplpj20hs0vkadr-169x300.jpeg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/51f8899ejw1fa13x3iplpj20hs0vkadr-577x1024.jpeg 577w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/51f8899ejw1fa13x41zvcj20hs0vkgqu.jpeg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-545216\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/51f8899ejw1fa13x41zvcj20hs0vkgqu.jpeg\" alt=\"51f8899ejw1fa13x41zvcj20hs0vkgqu\" width=\"400\" height=\"710\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/51f8899ejw1fa13x41zvcj20hs0vkgqu.jpeg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/51f8899ejw1fa13x41zvcj20hs0vkgqu-169x300.jpeg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/51f8899ejw1fa13x41zvcj20hs0vkgqu-577x1024.jpeg 577w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>@于建嵘：关于“精准扶贫”我提三个建议：一、要精确区分社保和致富。有些人因年龄和生理、自然条件，让他们享受基本的社会保障就行了，不要去瞎折腾他们。二、要精准区分作秀和实干。扶贫称为政绩，各种弄虚作假表明文章就多了。三、要精准区分施舍和权利。如何保障穷人的基本权利比施舍更重要。</p></blockquote>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[28993,8859,31745,8616]}